---
import { Layout, ProfileButton, Button } from "@continuum-ai/ui";
---

<Layout title="Continuum | The platform for no-code development and design.">
  <main class="px-8">
    <div class="section">
      <img src="/images/coding.svg" class="img-main" />
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h1>Community</h1>
        <p>
          At Continuum we believe in developers and the value they bring to each
          company. To support that, we developed products ranging from one of
          the most advanced website builders in the industry to analytics
          solutions and more. Lightweight and tailored just for your needs.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-row gap-4">
          <ProfileButton />
          <Button link="/docs" theme="light">Docs</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div class="row gap-lg section">
      <div class="column">
        <h1>Support</h1>
        <p>
          In order to help you reach your goals faster we developed solutions to
          support you as best we can, most of what we do is open source and if
          you need help, you can easily take a look at our <a href="/docs"
            >docs</a
          >.
        </p>
        <div class="row">
          <Button link="/signup" theme="dark">Learn More</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img src="/images/working-man.svg" class="img-main" />
    </div>
    <div
      class="row gap-lg section"
      style="flex-direction: column; display: flex;">
      <h1>Free. Forever.</h1>
      <p style="width: 100%;">
        We are a fully self-owned company, we don't have any investors to
        satisfy but you, you invest your time to make the web a more beautiful
        place and we want to support that as best we can. That means, no costs
        when making your first steps. <a href="/privacy/"
          >Learn about pricing and privacy.</a
        >
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-4">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-4">
            <img src="/logos/gyro.svg" />
            <h3>Gyro</h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            Export the source code at any time and use it freely in your
            personal or commercial projects. It's FREE and always will be.
          </p>
          <Button link="/projects/gyro/">Learn More</Button>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="row center gap-xl">
            <img src="/logos/meta.svg" />
            <h3>Meta</h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            Need some custom breakpoints? No problem, simply add them as you go
            and use them freely without any restrictions.
          </p>
          <Button link="/projects/meta/">Learn More</Button>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="row center gap-xl">
            <img src="/logos/deepend.svg" />
            <h3>Deepend</h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            Coming from a previous project and don't want to start all over
            again? No problem, we've got you covered, you can import a project
            or even add your own code at any time.
          </p>
          <Button link="/projects/meta/">Learn More</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  .section {
    @apply flex flex-col gap-4 lg:flex-row items-center mb-[160px];
  }

	.card {
		@apply border-2 rounded-lg border-slate-200 p-6;
	}
</style>
